Ask HN: Strategy to establish yearly personal objectives?
text:
If you work in an organization where you bonuses are tied to objectives that you have to establish ahead of time (like 6-12 months ahead of time), what is your strategy for determining (and phrasing the goals)

As a developer my idea is to establish objectives that are actually helping with personal growth and improve the organization, however I find it challenging to define goals that are realistic to complete in a changing environment and stay relevant after 6-12 months

What the hell is wrong with these people. If I wanted a loan,i would approach my bank and not some fincorp who would fleece me with 18% interests. Banks have much less interest rates
